flowchart TD
    Start([User Request]) --> Orchestrator[ORCHESTRATOR<br/>Core Engine]
    
    Orchestrator --> Parse[1. Parse Request<br/>Phân tích yêu cầu]
    
    Parse --> Plan[2. Plan Execution<br/>Lập kế hoạch]
    
    Plan --> Route{3. Route & Dispatch<br/>Định tuyến}
    
    Route -->|Research| RA[Research Agent<br/>Tìm kiếm thông tin]
    Route -->|Code| CA[Code Agent<br/>Thực thi code]
    Route -->|Chat| ChatA[Chat Agent<br/>Trò chuyện]
    Route -->|Tool| TA[Tool Agent<br/>Gọi APIs]
    
    RA --> Collect[4. Collect Results<br/>Thu thập kết quả]
    CA --> Collect
    ChatA --> Collect
    TA --> Collect
    
    Collect --> Validate{5. Validate<br/>Kiểm tra}
    
    Validate -->|OK| Format[6. Format Response<br/>Định dạng]
    Validate -->|Failed| Retry{Retry?<br/>< 3 lần}
    
    Retry -->|Yes| Route
    Retry -->|No| Fallback[Fallback<br/>Kết quả tốt nhất]
    Fallback --> Format
    
    Format --> Response([Final Response])
    
    %% Error handling
    RA -.->|Error| ErrorHandler[Error Handler]
    CA -.->|Error| ErrorHandler
    ChatA -.->|Error| ErrorHandler
    TA -.->|Error| ErrorHandler
    ErrorHandler -.-> Retry
    
    %% Monitoring
    State[(State<br/>Trạng thái)]
    Metrics[Metrics<br/>Giám sát]
    
    Orchestrator -.-> State
    Route -.-> State
    Collect -.-> State
    
    Orchestrator -.-> Metrics
    Validate -.-> Metrics
    
    style Orchestrator fill:#FFE5E5,stroke:#FF6B6B,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Parse fill:#FFF4E5,stroke:#FFB84D,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Plan fill:#FFF9E5,stroke:#FFD93D,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Route fill:#E5F5FF,stroke:#4DA6FF,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Validate fill:#E5FFE5,stroke:#6BCF7F,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Format fill:#F0E5FF,stroke:#B366FF,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style ErrorHandler fill:#FFE5E5,stroke:#FF9999,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    
    style RA fill:#E5F9FF,stroke:#4ECDC4,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style CA fill:#E5F3FF,stroke:#45B7D1,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style ChatA fill:#E5FFE9,stroke:#96CEB4,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style TA fill:#FFFBE5,stroke:#FFEAA7,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    
    style State fill:#F5E5FF,stroke:#D4A5FF,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Metrics fill:#FFE5D9,stroke:#FAB1A0,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    
    style Start fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#4CAF50,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Response fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#4CAF50,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
